     1тЖТ# Configuration
     3тЖТThis section details the configuration options available in the ***book.toml***:
     4тЖТ- **[General]** configuration including the `book`, `rust`, `build` sections
     5тЖТ- **[Preprocessor]** configuration for default and custom book preprocessors
     6тЖТ- **[Renderer]** configuration for the HTML, Markdown and custom renderers
     7тЖТ- **[Environment Variable]** configuration for overriding configuration options in your environment
