theme/syntax-highlighting.md
     1тЖТ# Syntax highlighting
     3тЖТmdBook uses [Highlight.js](https://highlightjs.org) with a custom theme
     4тЖТfor syntax highlighting.
     5тЖТ
     6тЖТAutomatic language detection has been turned off, so you will probably want to
     7тЖТspecify the programming language you use like this:
     8тЖТ
     9тЖТ~~~markdown
    10тЖТ```rust
    11тЖТfn main() {
    12тЖТ    // Some code
    13тЖТ}
    14тЖТ```
    15тЖТ~~~
    16тЖТ
    17тЖТ## Supported languages тАж
